Easyrec,is,an,open,source,recommender,system,that,can,be,integrated,into,a,website,via,a,REST,API,Developers,can,download,the,software,to,install,on,their,own,servers,or,use,a,hosted,version,The,API,exposes,functionality,such,as,viewing,buying,and,rating,items,viewing,recommendations,and,rankings,Responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON